title: 1-O 2017 Independence Referendum in Catalonia//The Reapers Song "Els Segadors" By A Sound Of Thunder
description:
The 1-O 2017 will surely happen to modern history, for being the day where voting without the acceptance of the leading state is a crime punished by force. Peaceful response to force, for wanting to exercise democracy ...
We will see how all this affects other European societies in the coming years.
